insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_36_h1ekxazo',36,'Amazon','"A good phone in the budget. Good things - 1 - AMOLED screen 2 - low weight 3 - network connectivity is excellent 4 - clean user interface/stock Android 5 - camera according to budget 6 - average design is fine. Fine - 1 - battery 5000 mah whereas other companies are currently offering 6000-7000 mah. 2- The refresh rate is 120 but only in the user interface. The app gets 60 Hz, which absolutely spoils the mood. 3- Software updates are nothing special. Must be at least 3+2. It''s an average phone. If you improve the software, you can become fantastic."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_36_h1nf3xrf',36,'Amazon','"Our relatives and we have been using Lava smartphones for last 4-5 years. Lava phones'' quality and durability is very good. They do not become sluggish or lose battery capacity. The only issues I see is that they are slow in providing security updates. And they have extremely few service centers as they provide home service, which is a bit costly. About this phone Lava Bold 2 5 G .. This is a relaunched version of Lava Amoled 2. The phone''s AMOLED display, stereo speakers, and overall fit and finish is very good. It takes around 90 minutes to charge from 0 to 100 % i.e., around one minute for every one percent of charge using the Lava charger that comes with the phone. The camera is decent, tuned for low-light photos and provides true colors. The phone comes with Android 15 with 1 year OS and 2 years security upgrades. Lava should add a battery protection feature to avoid the battery getting overcharged. The phone has background streaming feature and call recording. Overall, I highly recommend this phone. Good job by Lava..."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_36_h1w55hkw',36,'Amazon','"I bought the Lava Bold 2 on 28/09/2026. I have checked all the overall functions. The phone is good, though not excellent. A drawback is that there is no noise cancellation option during calls. The phone is lightweight and looks good. I am not concerned about the camera quality, so it is fine for me. I mainly prefer stock Android and smooth performance, and in that aspect, this mobile performs well. I bought the Lava Bold 2 mobile on 28/09/2026. I saw all the functions of this mobile. The mobile is good, but not very good. One drawback is that there is no noise cancellation feature when talking. This mobile is light and with a good appearance. I don''t care about the camera, so it is just right. I mainly saw stock Android and performance. In that sense this mobile offers good performance."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
