insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_7_hqvubcm',7,'Amazon','"I have always been from Xiaomi, a nest of bugs and errors everywhere, updates every month that fix one thing and break another. What made me look for another brand was the terrible proximity sensor. I switched to Realme and it''s another world. The best of Xiaomi but without those errors. The cell phone works very smoothly, the camera is the strong point, everything works as it should. Fast charging, good fluidity, great camera, the cell phone is beautiful, and the proximity sensor works. Android 14 with 2 major updates guaranteed. If they continue like this, I can''t get out of Realme."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_7_ha3yp9o',7,'Amazon','"Buying for about 3 weeks, so far nothing to complain about. Superb photo quality, smooth, good battery life, to see over time."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_7_h1n2rszo',7,'Amazon','"Realme 12 Pro 5G, a very good smartphone, makes great photos. Dual SIM, sold with its 67W charger and cable, a transparent plastic shell and a screen protector already installed on the phone. Too bad there is no possibility to put an SD card. But transferring data, photos and music from my old Realme 7 was done without a problem. Golden color, in reality is beige, imitation leather that is very soft to the touch. 5G network works great."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_7_h10a53gf',7,'Amazon','"I''ve been using my old phone for a long time and the difference in response is much better. In this price range, there are certainly cell phones that have a better camera or a slightly better processor, but I really liked the design. I also had a good experience with this brand. They run stably for years and the battery is retained for a long time. Ah yes, the RAM can be expanded in the settings with the internal memory plus 8GB, so it would then be 16GB RAM. So great for me."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
