insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_9_h6ak1b6',9,'Amazon','"bought the Moto G37 Power 5G mainly for its massive battery, and while the battery life is excellent, the overall experience has been disappointing. The HD+ display lacks sharpness and vibrant colors, making videos and browsing less enjoyable. Performance feels average, with occasional lag during multitasking and app switching. The camera is decent in daylight but struggles in low-light conditions. Charging speed is also slower than expected considering the large 7000mAh battery. Overall, apart from the battery backup, the phone does not offer the value and user experience I was expecting in this price range."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
