insert into comments (id,model_id,source,comment_text,comment_date) values ('Amazon_42_h1fexde2',42,'Amazon','"Battery: After one month of usage, I can give you genuine review about the battery. It will help you in decision making. I unplugged the charger at exactly 8 AM. After that I used all Apps for entertainment, office work app like google meet, excel, camera(atleast 500 times), oken scanner, whatsapp calls, msg, video calls, insta, x. Exactly - the mobile shutdown at 0% after 16 hours 40 minutes. The last 3% stood 37 minutes when I was watching YouTube. The last one minute still stood 16 minutes. 100% Charging it takes about about 1 hour. In 8 minutes, the battery charges 0 to 12%. Camera : Great, Dual Video Capture. Speaker: Mind blowing. Dolby Atmos. Display: Superb Grip: Fear of loosing if not used too of slim phone. Mobile very thin. Durability: Always use ring 💍 holder on back cover and a military grade back cover. Software: A MAJOR GLITCH- WHEN YOU SCROLL TWITTER VIDEOS IN CHROME, THEN PREVIOUS VIDEO SOUND KEEP COMING IN YOUR CURRENT VIDEO UNTIL OR UNLESS YOU GO BACK AND PAUSE THAT VIDEO AND THEN COME BACK TO PLAY YOUR CURRENT VIDEO. I THINK MOTOROLA NEEDS TO FIX THIS. Overall 3.8/5 just because of Camera, Battery, and Sound."',NULL) on conflict (id) do nothing;
